                     Why we use information across devices

                     One reason we use your information across devices[43] is to help us give you a
                     more personalized experience. For example, we might show you an ad on your
                     phone, and later you might use your laptop to click on the ad and buy the

https://mbasic.facebook.com/privacy/policy/printable/                                                   Page 31 of 111
Meta Privacy Policy - How Meta collects and uses user data                                           9/17/23, 9:02 PM



                     product. By combining that information across your devices, we can
                     understand what ads are relevant to you and help businesses measure how
